<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.2.5">
<l>kaṇṇaṉūr kaṇṇa puramtoḻuṅ kārikai,</l>
<l>peṇmaiyeṉ taṉṉuṭai yuṇmai yuraikkiṉṟāḷ</l>
<l>veṇṇeyuṇ ṭāppuṇṭa vaṇṇam viḷampiṉāl</l>
<l>vaṇṇamum poṉṉiṟa māva toḻiyumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What modesty does this beauty have, who worships at Kaṇṇapuram,</l>
<l>Kaṇṇaṉ’s city? She declares her own nature.</l>
<l>If [anyone] mentions the way he was tied, having eaten butter,</l>
<l>Her [pale] complexion, namely [its]  golden color, will leave.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
